Subject: Will Stealth pickup where it left off from a partial or cancelled scan
Description: when scanning a file system with the import partial results box checked, if we dont execute the bulk import job, will the next scan job pick up where it left off from a partial or cancelled scan?
Solution_Comment__c:
I provided the information to the customer:
Yes, the scan will resume from where it stopped. To ensure this, you need to check the 'Restart incomplete scans' option for the File System scan.
